  "text": "The AHP method was also compared with fuzzy analysis for the identification of potential energy wood terminal locations by [CITATION_1] ; the fuzzy analysis made it possible to evaluate the transition areas with continuous gradation more adequately. The authors of [CITATION_2] also used fuzzy analysis to define suitable areas for the installation of power plants and subsequently applied the mathematical allocation-location programming model to define the optimal installation site.",
